HEADWORD: Funded
<hw>Fund"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Existing
in the form of bonds bearing regular interest; <as>as, <ex>funded</ex>
debt</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Invested in public funds; <as>as, funded
money</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fundholder</ent>⟦br⟧
